## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="61549-102"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded>只發生事件時<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>控制項<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataSource%2A>屬性設定或其<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.VirtualMode%2A>屬性是`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61549-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event occurs only when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> control <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataSource%2A> property is set or its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.VirtualMode%2A> property is `true`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="61549-103">當您處理<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded>您指定的處理常式中的工具提示文字會顯示事件，每當滑鼠指標位於儲存格和控制項<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.ShowCellToolTips%2A>屬性值是`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61549-103">When you handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event, the ToolTip text you specify in the handler is shown whenever the mouse pointer is over a cell and the control <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.ShowCellToolTips%2A> property value is `true`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="61549-104"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded>事件很實用，當您想要顯示由目前的狀態或儲存格的值決定的工具提示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61549-104">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event is useful when you want to display ToolTips determined by the current state or value of a cell.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="61549-105"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded>事件也會發生值<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>擷取屬性，或是以程式設計的方式，或當滑鼠指標進入儲存格。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61549-105">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event also occurs whenever the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is retrieved, either programmatically or when the mouse pointer enters a cell.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="61549-106">您可以使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.ColumnIndex%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.RowIndex%2A>屬性來判斷狀態或儲存格值，並使用這項資訊來設定<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellToolTipTextNeededEventArgs.ToolTipText%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61549-106">You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.ColumnIndex%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.RowIndex%2A> properties to determine the state or value of a cell, and use this information to set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellToolTipTextNeededEventArgs.ToolTipText%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="61549-107">這個屬性會初始化儲存格的值與<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A>事件值會覆寫的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61549-107">This property is initialized with the value of the cell <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A> property, which the event value overrides.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="61549-108">處理<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded>事件時使用大量的資料，以避免效能的負面影響的設定儲存格<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A>多個資料格的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61549-108">Handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event when working with large amounts of data to avoid the performance penalties of setting the cell <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A> value for multiple cells.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="61549-109">如需詳細資訊，請參閱[縮放 Windows Form DataGridView 控制項的最佳作法](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/best-practices-for-scaling-the-windows-forms-datagridview-control.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61549-109">For more information, see [Best Practices for Scaling the Windows Forms DataGridView Control](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/best-practices-for-scaling-the-windows-forms-datagridview-control.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="61549-110">如需處理事件的詳細資訊，請參閱[NIB： 使用事件](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01e4f1bc-e55e-413f-98c7-6588493e5f67)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61549-110">For more information about handling events, see [NIB: Consuming Events](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01e4f1bc-e55e-413f-98c7-6588493e5f67).</span></span>  
  
   
  
